To prepare for the new Modern Warfare i started off with the one that kicked the series into new heights. Bare in mind I played the remaster version. This is a solid game even in today standards. A short but impactful campaign that has good Characters  great set pieces and tight gameplay. In terms of arcade action you can't get any better then this. The multiplayer is as good as it's always been with the creating a class and adding attachments and skins. There are problems of course. First off the loot box system is horrible. I hate it and screw Activision for putting it in here and screw them harder for making dlc maps for a remaster...dlc. Activision really don't care. And for me I played it through veteran and I get it. It's hardest difficulty but you do sometimes feel really unfair. I lost count how many times I'd fight the same enemy after a checkpoint restart and it always be random if I'd have time to shoot him or he'd snap to me and kill me quicker then I can aim down sight's. Our felt very unfair. Apart from that the game is great and set in stone a series that would make way for a generation of gamers. But what did you guys and gals think? Let me know and I'll see you guys... In the next post.  #game #Games #gaming #videogame #videogames #callofduty #callofduty4modernwarfare #callofduty4remastered

(45) “What’s wrong?” Abram snaps out of his rumination to turn to Cassandra who’s been intensely eyeing him. “What do you mean?” Cassandra  “Is it something that the villager said?” Abram shakes his head  “All he said is that we need to reach his son for a potion that will relieve his wife’s illness.” Cassandra  “Will it require grounded fungus and skeletal remains infused with demonic essence?” Abram scoffs  “The potion is suppose to help her breath  not infect her.” Cassandra  “Then why are you standing there looking so grave?” Abram ease the tension on his face to give a half-hearted grin  “I was thinking about.…about my parents.” Cassandra  “I can have Harding send a missive to Haven to see if Leliana received word from Ostwick.” Abram  “Thank you but not necessary.” Cassandra  “If that will give you a peace of mind to focus on…” Abram interrupts  “Any more news on the horse master?” Cassandra  “The farm remained unscathed from the fighting but I don’t know for how long. Give me a moment to talk to Harding…” Abram cuts her off  “Clearing the West Road will help our soldiers gain a foothold of the crossing. We must do so now.” Cassandra resigns with a sigh  “Yes  we should go.” At the corner of her eye  she sees Lucian walking by. Cassandra  “Scout Durand!” Lucian jogs up to Cassandra and bows  “Seeker.” Cassandra  “Gather the others. We’re heading to the West Road. You should also prepare.” Lucian speaks without looking up  “Understood. I just need to make a minor adjustment to my provision.” Cassandra  “Do what you must but do it quick.” “Yes ser.” Without a pause  Lucian dashes off. Abram trails Lucian with his eyes  “He seems a little nervous.” Cassandra  “I have faith that he will do well. I believe your siblings have been speaking with Scout Whittle by the entrance. . أكثر الشركات التي تدور حولها الشائعات، Rockstar Games وماهو مشروعهم القادم، هل هو Grand Theft Auto 6 أو Bully 2؟ - اخر الشائعات التي ظهرت على الإنترنت وبالتحديد موقع Reddit ذكرت بأن Grand Theft Auto 6 هي بالفعل تحت التطوير الكامل منذ ٢٠١٨ تحت الاسم الرمزي Project Americas، كما أشيع مسبقاً. - الاستوديو الذي يتولى تطويرها هو Rockstar North، بينما Rockstar India مسؤولون حالياً عن Bully 2 للجيل الحالي والقادم. - اللعبة تدور أحداثها في Vice City، والخريطة ستضم مدن ومستنقعات وجزر صغيرة وكبيرة، وستكون أفضل من Grand Theft Auto 5. كما سيكون هناك مهمات محددة في Liberty City - أسلوب اللعب سيكون شبيه بالجزء الخامس، لكن هناك اختلافات ستجعله مميز. تدور أحداث اللعبة في عدة فترات زمنية مختلفة واللاعب سيرى التغير الذي سيطرأ على المدينة والمركبات مع التقدم في القصة. - الطقس والتقلبات الجوية وتنوعها سيلعب دوراً كبيراً في هذا الجزء، لذلك توقع وجود صواعق، فيضانات، وأعاصير. - تماماً كالجزء الخامس، قرارتك واختياراتك هي التي ستحدد نهاية القصة. - كل هذي إشاعة، لكن شي جميل ودي يكون حقيقة، انتوا وش رايكم؟ 😍 . . . . . ‏#iMustPlay  #لعبة #العاب #قيمز #قميرز #تحدي #سوني #بلايستيشن #اونلاين #videogames #games #gamer #gaming #instagaming #instagamer #playinggames #online #instagood #xboxone #ps4 #sony #gta #gtaonline #rockstargames #play #playing #xbox #playstation4 #playstation

La storia di Thor indegno è stata già esplorata in passato. Cosa rende questa versione unica e differente?  Risposta: Cap è l’unico umano che Thor reputa degno di sollevare Mjolnir  ed ha fallito. Non solo  i “mortali” stanno discutendo tra di loro e non riescono a tornare uniti senza il loro Capitano. Anche Thor non riesce ad assumere il suo ruolo. Farà quindi una scelta molto interessante che avrà conseguenze indesiderate che riecheggeranno per tutta la campagna e si svilupperanno completamente nella storia del gioco.  Il Dio del Tuono ha abbandonato l’arma dopo aver fallito e presumibilmente non si sente più degno di brandirla  scelta che potrebbe portare a una storia che vada a esplorare il significato del fallimento per l’eroe  oppure una sorta di adattamento dell’acclamata run The Unworthy Thor(Indegno Thor). Finally it's #backlogbattler time and this time it's Fist of the North Star Lost Paradise on PS4. A game where you play as Kenshiro in another non canon adventure where knowing characters does help. In the tutorial you take out Shin  then go to the city of Eden where you become it's protector. You befriend the captain of the guard  get a truck you can ride around the sandbox in  do odd jobs like bartending  healing and managing a host club. You get random battles with goons everywhere which build up exp. You get references to the anime and manga everywhere. It's a wander around fighty drivey smash people's skulls in affair that plays a lot like Yakuza. It's mindless and can rack up the time easily. It's a fun game and if you like the series you'll love it. If you allow things to get on top of you however the main story will take a back seat and you'll find yourself just wandering around or driving around the desert looking for people to kill and items to get in the wastes. It's a fun game and I think it's worth the £30 asking price. #sega #sony #gaming #gamer #retro #arcade #franchise #retrocollectiveeurope #pickups #3d #adventure #rpg #action #3d #atlus #fistofthenorthstar #hokutonoken #kenshiro #playstation #ps4 #gamestergram #videogames #gamersunite #gamecollector #gamersofinstagram #jackrabbitgamer

É extremamente comum em um jogo você ter vários aspectos que se repetem  inimigos  objetos no cenário  itens e etc.  Por isso também é bastante comum nós podermos generalizar essas coisas e reutiliza-lás. … Pegue o exemplo de um personagem principal  ele vai estar EM TODAS AS FASES! Kkkk Agora imagine o fluxo -> Criar uma cena nova -> Colocar um SKSpriteNode -> Colocar a textura do personagem -> Seta as animações -> Os componentes -> Roda o jogo  Agora pense que seu jogo tem 30 fases distintas… Isso irá se repetir 30 vezes  kkkk.  Pior… Na 27 fase você percebeu que a escala podia ser melhorada  aumentar só um pouquinho  você terá que voltar em cada fase e ajustar isso  certo?  Pois bem  chega de fazer as coisas no Go horsing… trago a vocês a tal solução… SKReferenceNode Esse lindo  é um node que simplesmente é uma referência a uma outra cena! Então numa cena podemos fazer o personagem principal e em todas as outras 30 só referenciaremos ela. Relaxa que não pesa já que é só uma referência! E você também pode modificar a vontade dentro de uma cena específica se quiser algo especializado para tal cena  ou modificar na cena “mestre” e assim em todos os lugares que ela estiver sendo referenciada a modificação será aplicada! Per quanto possa essere un nuovo soulslike  Code Vein si conferma come un prodotto dall’anima originale e complessa  sfruttando l’estetica giapponese per proporre una delle esperienze più divertenti del genere. Attraverso a un sistema tanto accessibile quanto profondo e malleabile  vivere i panni di un Redivivo diventa una sfida più che gustosa che può essere adattata a qualsiasi tipo di giocatore. Ma il combattimento non è l’unico elemento invitante del gioco: la trama coinvolgente – anche grazie a un editor più che ottimo – e il ricco cast sono solo la portata principale di un mondo fatto di misteri  ricordi e colpi di scena sconvolgenti. Nonostante qualche comprensibile difetto  Bandai Namco e le menti dietro God Eater sono riusciti a produrre una nuova formula vincente  facendo nascere un’esperienza che si fa decisamente perdonare della lunga attesa.⠀ La mia Recensione di Code Vein per Game Division!⠀ -⠀ -⠀ #codevein #bandainamco #anime #vampire #soulslike #pc #ps4 #playstation #nintendoswitch #sony #xbox #mcirosoft #gamingfolk #gaming #gamer #game #videogame #videogames #videogioco #videogiochi #nerd #geek #singleplayer #multiplayer #player #playing #play #gamereview #recensione

Zelda Link’s Awakening – это ремейк классической Зельды с видом сверху  выпущенной ещё в далёком 1993 году на #GameBoy. На #NintendoSwitch игра перенесена практически с учётом всех нюансов  с улучшением графики и управления. Эта забота одновременно и плюс и минус игры. Бывалые геймеры будут рады и вспомнят былые времена  когда каждый секрет в подобных РПГ решался далеко не сразу и приходилось пробегать всю карту в течении нескольких часов  чтобы наконец понять  что и куда дальше. Но сегодняшние геймеры скорее назовут это проблемой геймдизайна  но никак не фишкой игры.  Что касается меня  то проблемы при прохождении я испытал буквально пару тройку раз. И это не проблемы с загадками в подземельях (они то как раз здесь очень крутые и их интересно решать именно самому)  а практически всегда это был вопрос «Куда же идти дальше?» Порой игра даёт лишь мелкие подсказки  которые не всегда очевидны. Решал это с помощью гайда для версии игры 1993 года (благо вся карта перенесена в ремейк 1 в 1) и зазрения совести от этого не испытываю. Пробегать всю карту и рубить мечом каждый кустик в надежде  что вот сейчас то под этим будет секретный вход в нужное подземелье… время дороже и времена не те :) В целом  ремейк однозначно понравился. Особо хочется отметить графику и стилистику проекта. Эстетика пластиковых игрушек выглядит замечательно  мир и персонажи очаровывают. #LinksAwakening способна вернуть вас в детство  даже если вы не играли в оригинал. А #Switch получил ещё один отличный эксклюзив в свою библиотеку.  #zelda #nintendoswitchgames #nintendo #linkzelda #portablegaming #rpggames #videogames #consolegaming #консольныеигры #видеоигры #обзорыигр #games #gaminglife

🎮 BARCODE BATTLERS II 時空を超えた戦士たち (Warriors who travelled in time) . Barcode Battlers was a series of Handheld consoles made by Epoch. . Barcode scanning toys and arcade games were extremely popular in the 90's Japan including the Datach Famicom add on  the later Digivices and Barcode Wars by Bandai. The strength of the Barcode Wars series was its connection to nintendo  allowing them to make exclusive barcode games with nintendo franchise such as Mario Bros and Zelda. . It also allowed players connect to their Super Famicom or original Gameboy via the 'Barcode Boy' to send data from the barcode cards into the Barcode Battler console games. . Barcode Battler was highly successful in Japan and even saw a release of western versions with alternative art and characters. . Did you go to the eshop and download yourself a copy of Gold Silver or Crystal?  Only getting the Red Gyradose as your first shiny? And want more?  What if i told you that in Gen 2 you can breed a shiny with a non shiny Pokemon Turning your odds from 1/8192 to 1/64 through breeding? --- Shiny hunting feels impossible through gen 2 and onward to some of us because of how high the odds are and theres no shiny charm till black and white 2.  Well In gen 2 theres something in the coding that makes Breeding a shiny with a mon shiny pop out shinies a bit faster  I believe its only breeding males with females of the same species or egg group  Anyway.  So you may not have a shiny ditto yet  Theres two ways to get one Random encounter one Or Use your red gyradose to trade to red blue or yellow use on a ditto only with mimic then catch and trade back to gsc  If you just have the Shiny Gyradose what can you breed with it?  One example is Dragonair  Another Tentacruel  A helpful thing to know is your egg groups  Gyradose is in the Water 2 and dragon egg group Dragonair is in the Dragon egg group Ekans is in the field and dragon egg group Tentacruel is in the water 2 egg group Ekans can breed with any field egg group mon such as mankey and primeape even eevee  I have done this shiny hunt method myself Getting myself various Shiny Pokemon  Since theres no abilities eggs will hatch relatively slow  Some hatch faster than others such as Magikarp hatching faster than lapras or snorlax  So my suggestion is trying magikarp first test your patience Then try Dratini or Something else.  If you're like "woah shit is this true?" Ever pick up a used copy of  Black  white  black 2 and white 2 and ever look at them like "Man i wish i could get the old event mons/items"  Well...what if i told you that In 2019 (2020) you can access them.  With 1 simple non game breaking/ bricking system exploit.  Called: the Dns server trick. This can be preformed with a 3ds family system and can also work for the original ds family line (not dsi line) ------ Without further adu gen 5. How to preform the trick: Step one: Go into your Wi-Fi settings  Step 2. Change the dns settings on your primary Wi-Fi connection Only the primary settings and insert these numbers 164.132.44.106.  Then hit okay and you're done! ---- You can preform this trick with gen 4 but it requires alot more effort that is difficult for me to explain so i have provided a link in my bio for how to do gen 4. ---- What mystery gifts can you get for gen 5?  Well....the mythicals for that gen. For black and white the liberty ticket to get victini Bw2 to get genesect Every single gen 5 Wi-Fi event is available  Even the Japanese  or other country events Note: the events are randomized and some will duplicate so its a gamble to get them all If you have missed any events  or wanted to relive nostalgia then this is the trick for you! These events can be transfered up to gen 7 through pokebank.  Also note for gen 4: if you get the Arceus  Shaymin and darkrai event they can be soft reset to get shiny  This also works for pokemon ranger shadow of almia and guardian signs to get the manaphy egg event mission ------ #pokemon #Bringbacknationaldex #grookey #sobble #scorbunny  #bea #allister #nessa #milo #drednaw #corviknight #wooloo #pokemonsword #pokemonshield  #pokemonswordshield #gamefreak #nintendoswitch #videogame #videogames #grookeygang #sobblesquad #scorbunnysquad #gamefreak  #nintendo #squirtle #curry #squirtlesquad #alcremie #nintendoswitch

Review Summary- Control ===================== SCORE: 9.1 ===================== You looking for a paranormal  sci-fi action game? This is the game for you! I can guarantee you haven't played anything quite like this before.  It has such a unique style and atmosphere  it oozes mystique  and has a certain stillness that keeps you on edge. It's reminiscent of the old Stanley Kubrick classics  so it wouldn't surprise me if that's where they got their inspiration from.  The combat is some of the most fun you'll have this year. Both the gunplay and psychic abilities are polished and each battle is a thrill. You'll always leave the battlefield in a state of choas  thanks to the destructible environments.  The story is full of mystery and will keep you invested  even if it can be a bit confusing at times  especially with the in-game terminology. Extra lore is told through an excessive amount of collectibles  so while there is a lot to learn about this fascinating world  you're constantly stopping to read yet again. It disrupts gameplay and I do wish it was handled more efficiently.  The side missions are just as much of a standout as the main story  with each one containing an interesting and unique storyline  and I always looked forward to each one.  Exploration was one of the weaker elements of the game  as it did get a little frustrating at times getting to where you needed to go. But this was made up by the amount of hidden secrets (and even some good puzzles) scattered around each area.  While it's a relatively short game  I still recommend this to anyone  as it's one of the better games this year. De 1859 com as cartas "Hanafuda"  seguindo até 1981 com o jogo Donkey Kong  onde foi a primeira aparição de Mario com o nome de Jumpman  até os dias atuais com Super mario Odyssey e o mais recente Mario Kat tour  a Nintendo completou 130 anos esse mês. Muitos dizem que a empresa é fraca diante da Sony com seu Playstation e da Microsoft com seu Xbox one  mas a verdade é que ela ano após ano vem trazendo novidades na maneira de se jogar vídeo game  sempre inovando no quesito experiência do jogador. Quem não se lembra do primeiro portátil  do seu primeiro sensor de movimento  do 3D sem óculos e do recente console híbrido!! São 130 anos de cenários belos  grandes aventuras  músicas que ficam na cabeça não importa quando tempo passe e de mínimos detalhes que superam muitas vezes qualquer poder gráfico e permite a cada jogador viver o mesmo jogo de maneiras diferentes. Fica aqui minha homenagem a essa grande empresa que fez e faz parte da vida de muita gente! Parabéns Nintendo 🎁🎊🎉 . . On-going review- Control ==================== My last post before I wrap up my review tomorrow. Now I've been mostly positive about this game so far  but it's not perfect  and there were a couple of things that held it back from true greatness.  I already talked about the excessive amounts of collectibles in my last post. It's fine to have a lot of extra lore  but surely there was a more efficient way to go about it.  My other main issue was how useless the map was. Maybe use it as a rough guide  but not to go exactly where you need to go. A lot of areas are multi-story  and the map just shows everything in one clump. If you're trying to get from one room to another  the map be more misleading than anything  and I did get frustrated quite a few times trying to get around.  When you think of maps from other games  like Resident Evil 2  they're laid out so clearly it helps makes exploration more fun because you're not wasting time looking at blank walls where the map says there should a doorway.  But I will admit my criticisms are fairly minor and didn't detract too much from the fun overall. So I must say  upon initial reaction to the ending of Tag  my reaction in my previous post still holds truth. However. - - After lots of reading  listening to radios  and watching YouTube videos  I can not say Tag is a bad map. Its truthfully brilliant once you give it some thought  and delivers a tragic ending no one saw coming. - - I will however  say that Tag is still a disappointing map to what they were building up. All we heard about since origins was “The Great War”. All through Blops4  it seemed to be the main point of focus leading up to Tag  giving most of us the impression we would be participating. Like I had hoped. - - Instead  we were completely thrown for a loop. Given something we just did not expect. So now this beckons the question  was this a bad thing? I dont think so. I actually think on Treyarch’s end  if their resources were as limited as its been rumored  was pretty brilliant. Because they pulled it off. - - Its a beautiful map. A nice reimagination of Call of the Dead  which really was one of my favorite maps ever. The radios are super interesting  the wonder weapons are pretty decent and easy to get  and it really plays like old school zombies. - - The ending makes sense too. Given all things considered and understanding their ultimate sacrifice  it is actually really beautiful. Its sad. It actually does make you think once you’re given more context. Once you understand  there was no way to end the cycle with all them existing. It didnt matter how they changed the future  their existence as a whole was the fracture that threw the very universe into chaos. - - Now i ask you  what do you think? I want to know your opinions  feel free to drop a comment or DM me personally. - - #blackops4 #blackops #zombies #tagdertoten #treyarch #playstation4 #ps4 #xboxone #callofduty #cod #modernwarfare #review #gaming #videogames #fortnite #pubg #nintendo #nintendoswitch

So… I just finished playing my first fire emblem three houses playthrough with the golden deer. The only other fire emblem game I played was fates: birthright but I never finished it and it did not grab my attention like three houses did. What I can say is that I loved this game  despite there being thing that I did not like/hated in it  but I  still loved the game through and through. I know that there are other routes  but I am planning on playing the GD route again and plan to recruit everyone into my house  so I will most likely watch a playthough on the other routes or play the other routes myself later in time. I can honestly say that this is one of the biggest if not the biggest Nintendo switch game of this year and I would highly recommend playing this game. I know there are people who do not like strategy rpg games and I understand that because I do not really like the genre like that  but give this game a chance at least. Alright I’m done talking and I will talk to you all later. . . . . . . . . . . . . •Cuando pasé Link’s Awakening para la Game Boy justo pasaba por un momento triste en mi vida  la pérdida de un ser querido. Y pues la historia de este juego me enseñó  de forma subjetiva  a lidiar con una pérdida  el irnos de un lugar en el que sabemos que no vamos a regresar jamás  el aprender a soltar y vivir con lo que esa persona o ese lugar nos ha enseñado. Por eso es un juego muy especial para mi. Y yo se qué la interpretación de este juego es muy subjetiva  y que quizá estoy volando mucho pero me gustaría analizar los videojuegos desde este ángulo también  un poco con teorías y formas distintas de verlos. ¿Qué dicen  les gustaría videos así? 🤔 . . . #linksawakening #nintendoswitch #nintendo #zelda #thelegendofzelda #link #videogames #videogame #youtube #youtube #games #videojuegos #gameboy

#fireemblem #fireemblemthreehouses #goldendeer #nintendo #nintendoswitch #videogames #videogamecollection  Ok  so I got this a few weeks back on day of release but only started playing it about four weeks ago  and man this fucking game had it's hooks in me from the start! I'm a big fan of this franchise so I had really been anticipating this one when it was announced about two years ago and it did not let down...well the ending could have been a bit better but that wasn't enough to ruin the experience I had. I can't recall the last time I put this much time into a game and it was a blast. Once the future dlc drops I'm probably gonna start a new game. This is a strategy RPG with life sim mechanics so it's not for everyone  but if you've ever been curious about these type of games this is a great game to start. ✌

... y ese motivo es poder usar las dos consolas como si fuera una. Al contrario que Nintendo 3DS  donde teníamos que eliminar y borrar los datos de una  para usar la otra  con la Cuenta Nintendo  no pasa. Podemos usar nuestra cuenta en Switch y Switch Lite  al mismo tiempo  compartiendo online  juegos digitales y el guardado de partidas en la nube. Solo una pega; la consola secundaria  necesita conexión a internet permanente  para poder jugar. Pero  he aquí la jugada; convertir en consola principal nuestra Lite  y como secundaria  la Switch original. Con este “setup” mi Switch original se queda en casa  con conexión permanente  y conectada a la TV  y la Lite la uso exclusivamente como portátil  y así poder jugar  sin necesitar conexión. Con el guardado en la nube  puedo descargar todas mis partidas y seguir jugando. Obviamente  tener los dos sistemas no es necesario. Pero si compartimos esta afición  tener ambas   puede ser una opción interésante  y disfrutar de las bondades de ambos sistemas. Por el momento  estoy llevándome la Switch Lite a todos lados  cuando antes  era más reservado  y me daba “cosa” llevármela según donde. En breves me voy de viaje y podré probarla a fondo. Espero haber arrojado algo de luz a vuestras dudas! #nintendoswitch #nintendoswitchlite #nintendo #brummelgames #gamer #videogames #nin10do #nintendoswitch #retrogamer #gamerroom #switch #nintendo3ds

Does anyone else Remember Minecade? Well  if you don't  then I can't say I blame you. Minecade was a server network that was popular in the Java edition of Minecraft for a short while. One of the most popular games on it was Super Craft Bross  which was basically Kit PVP with double jumping and special abilities. Sethbling  a Minecraft YouTuber who specializes in making mechanics and contraptions  was a pretty big face of the server for a while.  However  as time went by  things around the server started to go downhill. Updates for Super Craft Bros. were few and far between. Balancing issues and bugs were rarely if ever  fixed. To make things worse  Minecraft's popularity was in a lull. It was around this time I quit playing on Minecade because the games I liked just weren't fun to play anymore.  Fast forward to now. With Minecraft getting a bit of an extra life when it comes to mainstream popularity  I wondered what Minecade has been up to. Last I checked  they could barely break 50 players  and those players were mostly on a rather basic creative server. When I went to the website  all I found was  well  this. The website is a mess. I’ve also checked around a few forums and can’t find much.  So. What happened to Minecade? I’ll keep looking. #minecraft #videogames #videogame #game #gamer #gaming #playstation #ps4 #xbox #xboxone #pc #nintendo #nintendoswitch *puts on detective hat*

Espero que todos puedan jugarlo y lo disfruten tanto como yo disfruté haciéndolo. El nivel usa las distintas mecánicas que hay disponible para los Thwomps  y me aseguré que tenga fases llenas de emoción y diversión. Pese a que tiene una dificultad considerable (sobretodo para los más casuales) es posible completarlo luego de practicarlo  les recomiendo dedicarle tiempo. Algunas requerirán una prueba de habilidad  y otras les obligaran a pensar un poco más (pero hay pistas escondidas en todo el nivel). Si deciden emprender esta aventura extra  les deseo mucha suerte! I’ve been steadily picking at 'Fire Emblem Three Houses' for the past month or so and while I admit I haven’t quite finished the game I can say confidently that it is one of my favorites of the year. While I don’t have a ton of experience with the Fire Emblem series it's hard to imagine the diehards finding too much at fault with it’s core gameplay. The turn based “rock paper scissors” battles the series is iconic for are so engaging and addictive to play and beautifully presented. There’s something so epic about having the camera rapidly zoom in to the ground level of the battlefield so you can watch your characters duke it out. But I think the crowning achievement of this game is its story and narrative structure. You play as “The Professor” a sort of blank slate character who finds him or herself teaching at a prestigious military academy. In between battles you will fill your time lecturing and getting to know your students (who of course are your soldiers in battles) all the while completing side quests around the school. It’s essentially a lighter but more focused version of what the Persona series does. Within the first couple hours of play I found myself really caring for my students and motivated to prepare them as effectively as I could so they wouldn’t die in combat (yes perma-death is still a thing if you want it). This along with a storyline that evolves and twists based on your actions and choices makes for an immensely satisfying narrative experience. I beat Link’s Awakening last night! For the most part it was just as enjoyable as the original 1993 version that was my first 2D Zelda. Though I wouldn’t want it to return  the art style was charming and I did like it! Unfortunately  I do think more new features should have been added. Chamber Dungeons were a let down and figure collecting was pointless. The quality of life improvements were appreciated and I was grateful for more heart containers and seashells to hunt down and add to my total playtime. Most of the music was fantastic  with the tragic exception of Manbo’s Manbo which was hugely downgraded. Still I hope they release a soundtrack! $60 seems a bit unfair after everything is said and done  but I’m going to support the series I love best  regardless  in hopes of more remakes in the future. Febbraio 2018: ritratto di una studentessa stanca e pendolare che si gode uno sprazzo di sole invernale in uno splendido parco di Reggio Emilia. Stavo seguendo le ultime lezioni frontali per il percorso di formazione insegnanti e contemporaneamente scrivendo la tesi e facendo avanti e indietro tra Modena e Parma per questioni burocratiche. Valgono le mie occhiaie come testimoni oculari di quanto ho dichiarato?  Nostalgia a parte  dedico questo ricordo a tutti gli studenti  dalla primaria all'università  che ogni giorno affrontano mezzi pubblici  tomi di milioni di pagine ed ore su ore di lezioni. Anche quando vorreste farcire il muro di testate  dare fuoco agli zaini e fucilare i vostri professori  ricordate sempre che vince chi la dura  non chi si arrende! E concludo dicendo che se ce l'ho fatta io  che sono la pigrizia fatta a donna  ce la possono fare tutti😂. Buona fortuna  sempre e comunque. 1 ottobre 1954 IBM annuncia il computer Modello 705 L'IBM 705 è un computer di prima generazione  a valvole termoioniche. I primi esemplari vengono consegnati nel 1956. E' una macchina character-oriented (ovvero in cui il terminale comunica con l'elaboratore principale un carattere alla volta  contrariamente a quanto avviene nelle macchine block-oriented  in cui il terminale trasferisce blocchi di dati) con caratteri a 7 bit e parole a 35 bit (per contenere 5 caratteri). Il 705 Modello I viene equipaggiato con una capacità di archiviazione pari a 20.000 caratteri e costa circa 590.000 dollari. Il modello II e III hanno una capacità di archiviazione pari  rispettivamente  a 40.000 ed 80.000 caratteri. Può moltiplicare due numeri composti da dieci cifre in soli .0024 secondi. Il 705 è il primo computer distribuito commercialmente ad essere equipaggiato con una memoria a nucleo magnetico. Sostituisce l'IBM 702  che utilizzava una memoria costituita da un complesso di tubi a raggi catodici  in cui la sola unità aritmetica necessitava di 1.700 tubi a vuoto. #retroday #noiche #1980s #apple #atari #8bit #16bit #commodore #amstrad #msx #retrogaming #nerd #retrocomputer #retro #mac #computerhistory #geek #arcade #retrocomputing #videogames #retrogames #vintagecomputer #zxspectrum #vintage #retroconsole #machenesannoiduemila #AccaddeOggi #OnThisDay

Ieri ho deciso di aprire una nuova specie di rubrica che intitolerò : " Giochi epici che avrei dovuto giocare all'uscita ma che non ho mai giocato fino ad oggi''. Il protagonista di oggi e' Uncharted 4 A Thief's End. Wow. Sono rimasto davvero sorpreso dal prodotto di Naughty Dog  e mai avrei pensato che la saga di Uncharted potesse superare la bellezza e epicità raggiunta nel 2. Iniziando dai paesaggi   Uncharted 4 spinge PS4 a livelli mai visti primi. E' un gioco bello da vedere ma soprattutto ti dà l' impressione di essere vivo davanti i tuoi occhi. Per non parlare dell' Oceano e di come Naughty Dog abbiato lavorato per renderlo un paradiso per i giocatori. La chiusura delle storie legate a ciascun personaggio e' da Oscar   e ammetto di aver versato un paio di lacrime durante le scene finali. Questo e' l' esempio vivente di come un gioco passi da semplice mezzo di intrattenimento a vera e propria arte. Un applauso  Yesterday I decided to start a new journey which i named: "Epic games that I should have played when they came out but never did until now". Today's protagonist is Uncharted 4 A Thief's End. Wow. I was really surprised by Naughty Dog's product  and I never thought that the Uncharted saga could overcome the beauty and epicness achieved in second game. Starting from the landscapes  Uncharted 4 pushes PS4 to levels never seen before. It is so beautiful that there are times where the game almost seems to gain a life of his own. All the stories related to the different characters are closed wonderfully   and I have to admit that I cried a little during the ending scenes. This is the example of how a simple tool of entertainment can become art. Well done Naughty Dog. #play #playstation #ps4 #videogiochi #videogames #love #cuore #perfetto #uncharted #naughty #dog #nathan #arte #art #perfect #applausi #joy #wonderful #perfetto #likeforlike #follow

... y ese motivo es poder usar las dos consolas como si fuera una. Al contrario que Nintendo 3DS  donde teníamos que eliminar y borrar los datos de una  para usar la otra  con la Cuenta Nintendo  no pasa. Podemos usar nuestra cuenta en Switch y Switch Lite  al mismo tiempo  compartiendo online  juegos digitales y el guardado de partidas en la nube. Solo una pega; la consola secundaria  necesita conexión a internet permanente  para poder jugar. Pero  he aquí la jugada; convertir en consola principal nuestra Lite  y como secundaria  la Switch original. Con este “setup” mi Switch original se queda en casa  con conexión permanente  y conectada a la TV  y la Lite la uso exclusivamente como portátil  y así poder jugar  sin necesitar conexión. Con el guardado en la nube  puedo descargar todas mis partidas y seguir jugando. Obviamente  tener los dos sistemas no es necesario. Pero si compartimos esta afición  tener ambas   puede ser una opción interésante  y disfrutar de las bondades de ambos sistemas. Por el momento  estoy llevándome la Switch Lite a todos lados  cuando antes  era más reservado  y me daba “cosa” llevármela según donde. En breves me voy de viaje y podré probarla a fondo. Espero haber arrojado algo de luz a vuestras dudas! #nintendoswitch #nintendoswitchlite #nintendo #brummelgames #gamer #videogames #nin10do #nintendoswitch #retrogamer #gamerroom #switch #nintendo3ds

История Орды. Начало. Жила на планете Аргус раса эредаров (внезапное начало истории орды  да?).И правил этой расой совет экзархов в лице трёх деятелей  таких как Архимонд  Кил’Джеден и Велен.  Правили они мудро и было у них всё хорошо  но до одного момента. Дело в том  что Саргерас устал самолично управлять большим количеством демонов (они же все разномастные  не особо покорные и не особо умные) и понял  что ему нужны полководцы. Тут то история Саргераса и эредаров пересекается  ибо поехавший титан обратил внимание на высокоцивилизованную расу.  Явившись к экзархам в лице сущности светлой и сияющей  он сделал им предложение знаний  силы  просветления и много другого. Архимонд и Кил’Джеден с радостью приняли его предложение  однако Велена терзали смутные сомнения. Особенно после того  как ему (Велену) явилось видение (ах да  забыл сказать  Велен пророк) того  что произойдёт с его народом  если они примут предложение Саргераса (красная кожа  злые морды  короче трэш и угар). . أكثر الشركات التي تدور حولها الشائعات، Rockstar Games وماهو مشروعهم القادم، هل هو Grand Theft Auto 6 أو Bully 2؟ - اخر الشائعات التي ظهرت على الإنترنت وبالتحديد موقع Reddit ذكرت بأن Grand Theft Auto 6 هي بالفعل تحت التطوير الكامل منذ ٢٠١٨ تحت الاسم الرمزي Project Americas، كما أشيع مسبقاً. - الاستوديو الذي يتولى تطويرها هو Rockstar North، بينما Rockstar India مسؤولون حالياً عن Bully 2 للجيل الحالي والقادم. - اللعبة تدور أحداثها في Vice City، والخريطة ستضم مدن ومستنقعات وجزر صغيرة وكبيرة، وستكون أفضل من Grand Theft Auto 5. كما سيكون هناك مهمات محددة في Liberty City - أسلوب اللعب سيكون شبيه بالجزء الخامس، لكن هناك اختلافات ستجعله مميز. تدور أحداث اللعبة في عدة فترات زمنية مختلفة واللاعب سيرى التغير الذي سيطرأ على المدينة والمركبات مع التقدم في القصة. - الطقس والتقلبات الجوية وتنوعها سيلعب دوراً كبيراً في هذا الجزء، لذلك توقع وجود صواعق، فيضانات، وأعاصير. - تماماً كالجزء الخامس، قرارتك واختياراتك هي التي ستحدد نهاية القصة. - كل هذي إشاعة، لكن شي جميل ودي يكون حقيقة، انتوا وش رايكم؟ 😍 . . . . . ‏#iMustPlay  #لعبة #العاب #قيمز #قميرز #تحدي #سوني #بلايستيشن #اونلاين #videogames #games #gamer #gaming #instagaming #instagamer #playinggames #online #instagood #xboxone #ps4 #sony #gta #gtaonline #rockstargames #play #playing #xbox #playstation4 #playstation

Sometimes you just have to take a day and focus on your hobby. I love gunpla and model kits. I took the diamond loot chest Sanctuary 3 model and did a full repaint on the shell. Took it from a bland tan/grey to a high polish brushed silver. Then I went in an weathered the whole ship slightly  to provide accents. I painted all the windows and the bridge French blue for a better pop  and detailed the mechanical elements with red along with finally adding the decals. Я и море. Когда впервые встречаешь его такое тихое и спокойное  и в спокойствие своём величественное ..всегда я чувствую себя дома с ним  я дышу вместе с приливами и отливами  также гармонично..как и волны. Как в колыбели тебя баюкает мама. Когда море волнуется  сразу ощущаешь хрупкость мира как в каждую секунду где-то происходит исход и что-то неизбежное .. И никогда не изведать его глубины  оно скрывает столько тайн и манит и манит... И раскрывает нас самих. От моря пахнёт одиночеством. И в конце пути человек остаётся один на один с собой и со своими мыслями   которые как волны накатывают порой превращаясь в цунами  руша все или наоборот затихая в штиль. Старик и море 🌊 Хемингуэй. Finally it's #backlogbattler time and this time it's Fist of the North Star Lost Paradise on PS4. A game where you play as Kenshiro in another non canon adventure where knowing characters does help. In the tutorial you take out Shin  then go to the city of Eden where you become it's protector. You befriend the captain of the guard  get a truck you can ride around the sandbox in  do odd jobs like bartending  healing and managing a host club. You get random battles with goons everywhere which build up exp. You get references to the anime and manga everywhere. It's a wander around fighty drivey smash people's skulls in affair that plays a lot like Yakuza. It's mindless and can rack up the time easily. It's a fun game and if you like the series you'll love it. If you allow things to get on top of you however the main story will take a back seat and you'll find yourself just wandering around or driving around the desert looking for people to kill and items to get in the wastes. It's a fun game and I think it's worth the £30 asking price. #sega #sony #gaming #gamer #retro #arcade #franchise #retrocollectiveeurope #pickups #3d #adventure #rpg #action #3d #atlus #fistofthenorthstar #hokutonoken #kenshiro #playstation #ps4 #gamestergram #videogames #gamersunite #gamecollector #gamersofinstagram #jackrabbitgamer

Pickpocketing is also interesting in this game. You have to get close to a person and while remaing undetected  reach into their pockets.  The timer at the start determines how many seconds you will get to rummage around looking for items. The longer you can hold out the longer you get to look.  As the timer goes up  depending on your skill and your marks various attributes  it gets more dangerous to keep rummaging. The background of the timer will start to turn red when you are close to getting caught.  Once you have completed the timer mini game successfully you use what time you have earned to go through the various items and uncover what they are. You pick what you want and then have to navigate to the exit.  You manage to do that before time runs out and you have successfully pickpocketed someone!  Protip: To level Pickpocketing up faster and easier  do it to people who are sleeping! . . . . . . . . . . #pickpocket #kingdomcomedeliverance #pickpocketing #kingdomcome #medieval #rpg #gaming #videogames #simulation #xboxgamepass #XboxShare #XboxOneX #gamepass #rogue #thief #stealing #ninjaskills

✨Ocarina Of Time MasterQuest✨ ———————————————————————- . [2003 - Gamecube CAN - Aventure] . 🇫🇷 Voici l’une de mes fiertés  en tant que fan de Zelda  dont mon top 1 JV Ocarina Of Time  une version devenue rare et atypique. OOT avait été porté sur Gamecube notamment en bonus avec Wind Waker  et dans une compile collector exclusive du club Nintendo  mais pas que. Je présente ici la version Canadienne de OOT + Master Quest  c’est à dire la version experte  difficile  du jeu original. Un nouveau challenge plus ardu pour les adeptes du jeu en quête de défi (monstres plus féroces  mode miroir permanent  santé faible etc.) Bref une pièce que j’ai eu le flair de rentrer il y a deux ans environ avant que sa cote ne s’envole  car il existe une version US only  moins rare  mais cette version CAN devient assez balèze à dénicher à prix honnête! Bref la passion du collectionneur c’est aussi ça  miser et investir sur des pièces en devenir  sur des pépites dormantes  et qui plus est  pour l’un de mes Set favoris : Zelda. . • Connaissez vous cette version de Ocarina Of Time? Quelle sont vos trouvailles les plus originales en rétro qui sont devenues ultra rares par la suite? . 🇬🇧 I’m very proud to have this uncommon Ocarina Of Time  Canadian version in my collection. It became pretty rare since few years  I bought it 2 years ago. OOT was adapted on Gamecube as a bonus game included in Wind Waker  but also on one gamein US and Canada with this compilation. I’m happy to possess Canadian one  espacially because OOT and Zelda is one of my most important collection’s target. And It’s always great for a collector to find original pieces at the good moment before they become rare and expansive. . • Do you know this OOT version? . ——————————————————————— #thelegendofzelda #zelda #nintendo #gamecube #videogames #gamecollection #videogamecollection #retrocollective #gamer #videogaming #retrogaming #retrogames #gaming #gamer #retrocollectiveus #retrocollector #instagaming #jeuxvideo #ninstagram #igersnintendo #gamerguy #geeklife

NETFLIX HA RILASCIATO IL PRIMO TEASER DI STRANGER THINGS 4. OK  È SOLO IL LOGO NEL SOTTOSOPRA  MA PUÒ ESSERCI GIÀ QUALCOSA DI INTERESSANTE DI CUI PARLARE. Innanzitutto ci tengono a sottolineare che non saremo più a Hawkins  ma non ci viene detto allora dove la storia si sposterà. Ecco però che partono le mie teorie. Abbiamo tre cose da tenere a mente: il Sottosopra che divora il logo  la scritta "Non siamo più a Hawkins" e il suono delle campane. Che sia proprio il Sottosopra l'ambientazione in cui la storia si svolgerà? A fine della terza Undici ha "perso" i poteri  magari c'è qualche collegamento con il Sottosopra  anzi  di sicuro. Pensateci  a costo di trovare un espediente credibile  non sarebbe l'ora di esplorare in modo approfondito il Sottosopra? Inventarsi qualcosa di nuovo di cui prima non se ne sentiva parlare? Anche perché non manca proprio tanto ad una stagione finale eh... E per quanto riguarda le campane  potrebbero indicare un periodo dell'anno ben preciso? Un luogo  magari. Ma cerchiamo di rimanere con i piedi per terra. Magari i ragazzi sono semplicemente in un'altra città  anzi  lo sono  come abbiamo visto sempre nel finale della 3. Ma allora io mi chiedo  ha senso far cambiare città ai protagonisti  ribadire che non saremo più nell'ormai iconica Hawkins  se non giustifichi a livello di novità la cosa? Cosa mi cambia a me se accadono le stesse cose che sono sempre accadute ma in un posto diverso? Sfruttate la novità in modo impeccabile  non decente  impeccabile. Fate in modo che almeno ci siano davvero elementi mai visti prima dato che ci troviamo in una città diversa. Io do credito a questa ultima ipotesi  anche se esplorare a fondo il Sottosopra sarebbe una buona cartuccia ~Lore  #marvel #geek #davidharbour #avengers #milliebobbybrown #serietv #supereroi #dc #dccomics #ironman #strangerthings4 #strangerthings #culturapop #film #movie #marvelstudios #starwars #cinema #finnwolfhard #videogiochi #gatenmatarazzo #superhero #netflix #videogames #games #comics #fandom #disney #netflixitalia #instaitalia

Ah shit here we go again  Il 24 ottobre del 2004  il videogioco di azione Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas  sviluppato dalla Rockstar Games fu rilasciato per Playstation 2. Subito dopo il filmato di apertura  in cui il personaggio principale Carl "CJ" Johnson viene molestato e ricattato da degli agenti di polizia corrotti  il gioco inizia con lui che si ritrova in un quartiere ostile della città e dice: "Ah merda  eccoci di nuovo qui. Il posto peggiore al mondo  il paese di Rolling Heights Ballas. Non rappresento Grove Street da 5 anni  ma ai Ballas non gliene frega niente." La scena non ha avuto alcuna diffusione significativa online fino al 2015  quando venne ricaricata su YouTube e iniziò ad essere usata come immagine di reazione. Tuttavia raggiunse una ancora maggiore notorietà solo nel settembre del 2018  quando si diffuse su Reddit. Il meme è ad oggi ancora uno tra i più utilizzati. Про Gears 5 было до релиза известно не так много: тухленькая пиар-кампания и толком не представленный геймплей наталкивали на дурные мысли. Однако игра вышла и развеяла все сомнения: геймплей все так же бодр и весел  все стреляет  звучит и бегает отменно  визуально - мое почтение (это вообще одна из самых красивых игр линейки Xbox)  история в целом неплоха  но вполне стандартна. Даже выдвигание на передний план Кейт Диаз  дебютировавшей в прошлой части смотрится довольно необычным шагом для такой истории. Также стоит отметить полуоткрытые локации во втором и третьем актах игры: мы можем кататься по более открытому коридору и выполнять дополнительные задания. Имплементированы они довольно осторожно: выполнять их никто не заставляет и они довольно однообразны  однако за счет занимательных диалогов между персонажами во время их выполнения заниматься ими ненапряжно и бонусом можно получать детали для улучшения робота Джека  который прокачивается  помогает нашим героям и является постоянным участником всех событий (за него даже играть можно). Из минусов я бы отметил недостаток зрелищных и запоминающихся ситуаций (они есть  но их мало) да и хотелось бы больше новых элементов в привычную концепцию шестеренок. В целом это типичная вторая игра трилогии и пока лучшая часть от The Coalition (конечно  она уступает трилогии от Epic Games  но держится на ее фундаменте очень крепко)  поиграть в нее определенно стоит (особенно в коопе) 8/10 #gears5 #xboxone #videogames #thecoalition

Il vantaggio  come ben sappiamo  sarà legato a caricamenti più rapidi: chi non ama attendere meno per iniziare a giocare? Di certo Chameleon Games  creatore di Tamarin – platform action ispirato dai classici di Rare -  è un fan dell’SSD di PS5 e  in una recente intervista rilasciata ai microfoni di GamingBolt  ha spigato perché. Omar Sawi  capo dello studio  ha affermato: “È grandioso perché i tempi di caricamento sono una rottura. È difficile nasconderli  inoltre. Abbiamo dovuto pensare molto a come farlo nell’attuale generazione  poiché non volevamo schermate di caricamento. Sin dalla sua prima comparsa in forma cartacea  It è stato riconosciuto come un caposaldo del genere Horror se non il suo maggiore esponente.  Considerato il capolavoro di Stephen King  il libro scritto nel 1986 ha avuto la sua prima trasposizione cinematografica nel 1990  con una miniserie in due episodi che a sua volta è stata manifesto dell’horror per molti anni.  Ai giorni nostri però  l’eco del successo di It non si è spento  e a concludere il ciclo di remake cinematografici iniziato nel 2017 con IT: Chapter One  arriva puntuale il 5 settembre prossimo IT: Chapter 2  con il non semplice compito di chiudere ancora una volta il baule di ricordi e terrore riemersi nelle menti dei fan e dei neofiti che si sono avvicinati timorosi ai cinema per diventare amici dell’affabile Pennywise. GPU integrata Intel Gen12 con 96 Execution Unit avvistata su CompuBench - Le GPU integrate Intel Gen12  basate sulla nuova architettura Xe (che sarà il cuore anche delle GPU dedicate)  rappresenteranno per ammissione della stessa azienda un cambiamento epocale. L’ISA sarà profondamente rinnovata  ma allo stesso tempo Intel aumenterà probabilmente anche il numero delle Execution Unit (EU)  cosa che in casa AMD e Nvidia abbiamo visto essere sempre un buon modo per incrementare le prestazioni rispetto alle generazioni precedenti.  Il maggior numero di EU non è solo un’idea logica  ma in queste ore sembra essere qualcosa di più: su CompuBench è infatti passata una non meglio identificata GPU integrata Intel Gen12 con 96 Execution Unit  più delle 64 EU integrate nelle CPU Ice Lake con grafica Gen11 o delle 72 EU dell’Iris Pro P580 vista in alcune CPU Xeon del 2016.  Il numero è inoltre decisamente superiore rispetto alla UHD 630 con 24 EU integrata nelle CPU consumer più diffuse. [CENAS MARCANTES]  Sabemos que a série de Game Of Thrones é conhecida por não dar estrela aos seus protagonistas  todos eles vivem em um mundo real onde a morte não é algo intocável pra nenhum deles. Resumindo  nenhum dos personagens de Game Of Thrones estão livres da morte  e a série é conhecida assim  por matar seus personagens  tanto como seus personagens sem muito peso  até o os protagonistas. E porque o game de Game Of Thrones seria diferente?  Games Of Thrones da Telltale é um game lançado no dia 2 de dezembro de 2014  o game conta com alguns personagens da série  como Jon Snow  Daenerys entre outros.. O jogo não é diferente de nenhum dos jogos da Telltale  nele também temos a função de escolhas  na qual essas escolhas influenciam no decorrer da história  o game é conhecido por causar inúmeras emoções em seus jogadores e existe uma cena que pode ser considerada umas das escolhas mais difíceis do game. Asher e Rodrick são personagens jogáveis do game  e também irmãos. Asher vivia num lugar distante de sua família e Rodrick é nomeado lorde de sua casa. Em um certo ponto do game acontece o reencontro dos dois irmãos e é algo muito legal de se ver  porém esse reencontro não duraria muito  Rodrick e seus homens são emboscados por um exército inimigo e a única forma de sobreviver seria fugindo  e nesse momento é quando o jogo te dá a escolha mais difícil do game  um dos dois irmãos deveria morrer pra que sua casa sobreviva  então  o game te dá a escolha de quem sacrificar. O game tem inúmeras cenas de emoções  tanto boas como ruins  mas provavelmente essa cena é uma das mais marcantes pra quem jogou o game.  Obs: esse é um dos jogos mais emocionantes que já joguei e é um dos meus jogos preferidos  até hoje. BIONIC COMMANDO: In 1987 arcade gamers became special forces soldiers in order to infiltrate an enemy base and stop the launch of a devastating missile attack.  A classic action platform game from Capcom this is one of the coolest games of its time thanks to all jumping being removed in favour of using an extendable arm to move around the level.  Converted to a ton of home computers including the Amiga  Atari ST  C64  ZX Spectrum and Amstrad CPC this also came to the NES although that version was very different.  Did you ever play this game? Febbraio 2018: ritratto di una studentessa stanca e pendolare che si gode uno sprazzo di sole invernale in uno splendido parco di Reggio Emilia. Stavo seguendo le ultime lezioni frontali per il percorso di formazione insegnanti e contemporaneamente scrivendo la tesi e facendo avanti e indietro tra Modena e Parma per questioni burocratiche. Valgono le mie occhiaie come testimoni oculari di quanto ho dichiarato?  Nostalgia a parte  dedico questo ricordo a tutti gli studenti  dalla primaria all'università  che ogni giorno affrontano mezzi pubblici  tomi di milioni di pagine ed ore su ore di lezioni. Anche quando vorreste farcire il muro di testate  dare fuoco agli zaini e fucilare i vostri professori  ricordate sempre che vince chi la dura  non chi si arrende! E concludo dicendo che se ce l'ho fatta io  che sono la pigrizia fatta a donna  ce la possono fare tutti😂. Buona fortuna  sempre e comunque. Microsoft non si fida dei produttori di SSD  la cifratura software di BitLocker sale in cattedra - Dall’introduzione del famigerato Windows Vista  i sistemi operativi di Microsoft integrano BitLocker  una funzionalità che consente di crittografare l’intera partizione del sistema operativo al fine di proteggere le informazioni. Il tipo di crittografia usata da Bitlocker – hardware o software – è impostata tramite Criteri di Gruppo. Se disponibile  si usa la cifratura hardware standard. Molti SSD e hard disk offrono (o dicono di offrire) infatti sistemi di cifratura dei dati  che dovrebbero svolgere in hardware il compito di BitLocker. Di conseguenza BitLocker lasciava campo libero alle tecnologie integrate nei controller  dando credito alle parole dei produttori e sgravando la CPU da un carico importante.  Il problema è che a volte i sistemi di cifratura hardware integrati non fanno ciò per cui sono preposti  e se lo fanno lasciano la porta aperta al furto di dati da parte di malintenzionati come emerso in passato. La primera entrega de Arc the Lad  una impresionante saga de juegos RPG táctico en el que quizá no muchos recuerdan  pero tuvo una gama muy robusta en su tiempo  quizá no llegó a tener la pegada y la fama como otras franquicias de su mismo género o del JRPG. Pero fue una de las mejores de la primera PlayStation de Sony. Siempre estaban las mismas críticas de siempre de "medios profesionales" Del ámbito  criticando que sus gráficos eran de una generación pasada  que no eran meritorios de estar en una consola mucho más potente. Pero fuera de críticas que no hacen más que ensuciar grandes juegos y hacer que muchos jugadores no disfruten o se embarquen en juegos desconocidos  la saga siempre se ha presentado en un diseño curioso al más puro estilo clásico  con una jugabilidad muy cercana a Bahamuth Lagoon o Fire Emblem. También hay que remarcar  que su fama fue tal que  decidieron crear una serie de anime basado en el videojuego  algo muy curioso  ya que realmente se acostumbra a ver una práctica contraria  crear un videojuego referente alguna serie o anime. Muy recomendado para los fans del JRPG  RPG táctico o gente que haya visto el anime y que desconocía que venía de una saga de videojuegos. - Recordad que la tienda de accesorios gaming  móviles  consolas y videojuegos y mucho más @patasys  me ha hecho su embajador  así que aquí tenéis mi link especial: www.patasystem.com/retrofantasy y las seis primeras personas que ordenen algo tendrán envió gratis con el Código FREESHIPPINGRETROFANTASY. ¡Ya me dirás si has encontrado algo de tu gusto!. - #retrocollective #retrogamer #retrogames #retrogamescollector #retrovideogames #retrogaming #retrocollector #videogaming #videogamescollective #videogamescollector #videojuegos #videogames #instagaming #instagames #instagamerspain #gaming #games #gamescollector #sony #playstation #manga #jrpg #anime

Here comes a new challenger! - - - - - - - - - - - - “SEGA Versus City” es una máquina arcade tipo Candy un poco diferente. Propone un insólito concepto de recreativa siamesa con dos pantallas. Una única placa se encarga de dividir el audio  el vídeo y el control de ambos lados. Ello permite jugar simultáneamente a dos personas en la misma máquina sin tener que compartir panel de control. - - - - - - - - - - - - Una de las curiosidades más destacadas es la marquesina superior situado en cada lado. Incluye una marquesina con el texto “WINNER!” que se ilumina para indicar el vencedor de la partida. Se trata  pues  de una arcade orientada al juego competitivo. En su época  era común verla con “Street Fighter” en todas sus versiones  pese a que Capcom nunca programó ningún juego que pudiera aprovechar estas funcionalidades especiales. - - - - - - - - - - - - Esta rareza proveniente de Japón 🇯🇵 acaba de aterrizar en #LaNau. In 1993 I was at mates house with friends having a game night. We game all night  few beers  mosty multi player and always Mega Drive. Though this night was different. ============== Someone had taken along their Super Nintendo to show a game they had just purchased. My eyes rolled. I only play Sega games 🙄 so with pain I took honour of leaning over back of the TV and fishing to unplug the trusted Mega Drive. ============== Being a Sega fanboy I had yet to experience or even see a SNES game in action so my care level was probably zero. Yet my mind was soon to change and tbh it was easy. While we were all taking turns on a Super Mario level I could feel myself getting hooked.Then after playing the likes of Pilot Wings  Mario Kart and F-Zero...I was sold. ============= The very next day I hit the shops and picked up this very SNES  a copy of Super Mario All Stars ....and every Mode 7 game that I could get my hands on 😏👍 ============== Super Mario All Stars was the very first game I played on the SNES and I guess it made me never choose sides again. 😎🤝😎 ============ Was there ever a game that made you rush out and buy a console?? . . . . . . . . . #nintendo #snes #supernintendo  #supermario #supermarioworld #supermarioallstars #retrogamer #retrogamers #retrogaming #retrogamingcommunity #oldschoolgaming #videogames #gamecollector #gamerguy #instagamer #gamer #gamerlife #gaming #gamersofaus #aussiegamers #nintendopower #nin10do #nes #nintendolife #nintendogamer #nintendogaming

💖𝑫𝒆𝒕𝒓𝒐𝒊𝒕: 𝑩𝒆𝒄𝒐𝒎𝒆 𝑯𝒖𝒎𝒂𝒏💖 This is my fav one. You guys can't even imagine how many emotions I experienced. Every single choice is in your hands  and we're not even talking about one or two choices. You're actually able to mold the ENTIRE story  just by listening to your heart. The most important thing here  is that you realize what your heart and mind say. You're full of anger: you decide to start a war. You're a pacific person: you try to talk to people and let them feel what you feel. You need to take care of your characters  otherwise you will lose them and you won't be able to play the story with them anymore. So yeah  let's say that it's all in your hands  this is not a normal story. You choose who you are. This story makes you realize so many personal things  that's why I love this game more than everything. Hope you liked it as much as I did. ꧁꧂ Questo è il mio gioco preferito  in assoluto. Ragazzi  non potete minimamente immaginare quante emozioni mi ha regalato questo gioco. Ogni singola scelta è nelle vostre mani  e non stiamo parlando di una o due scelte. Questo gioco è in grado di farvi plasmare l'INTERA storia  ogni singola scelta può stravolgere tutto. Dovrete prendervi cura dei vostri personaggi  altrimenti rischierete di perderli e non poterli più utilizzare per tutto il resto della storia. La cosa più importante di questo gioco è che  scegliendo tutto ascoltando il vostro cuore  vi renderete conto di che persone siete  di cosa vi dice l'istinto. Siete pieni di rabbia? Deciderete di iniziare una guerra. Siete persone pacifiste? Parlerete alle altre persone cercando di fargli sentire ciò che VOI sentite. The Hori Split Pad Pro by Daemon X Machina for Nintendo Switch under official license is certainly a great product capable of perfectly reproducing the convenience of a traditional controller even in portability. Obviously this is a product designed only for comfort wherever you want  in fact it is lacking in both vibration and movement sensors. Choices that a little displease us but that are justified by the desire to avoid overdoing weight. For those looking for "pro" comfort even outside the home this is certainly the right product. . Lo Split Pad Pro di Hori griffato Daemon X Machina per Nintendo Switch sotto licenza ufficiale è certamente un ottimo prodotto capace di riprodurre alla perfezione la comodità di un controller tradizionale anche in portabilità. Ovviamente questo è un prodotto pensato per la sola comodità ovunque si voglia  infatti è sprovvista sia di vibrazione sia di sensori di movimento. Scelte che un po' ci dispiacciono ma che vengono giustificate dalla volontà di evitare di eccedere troppo col peso. Per chi cerca comodità da "pro" anche fuori casa questo è certamente il prodotto giusto. . 🕹️📺🎮❤️👍👌 #videogames #games #gamer#instagaming #photooftheday #20likes #amazing #look #instalike #igers #picoftheday #technology #nintendo #supermario #zelda #collectibles #epic #handson #instagood #gamestagram #thelegendofzelda #nintendoswitch

Akumajou Dracula X: Chi no Rondo  AKA Castlevania: Rondo of blood.  The game was released in japan on oct 29th  1993. An amazing halloween gift for our Japanese buddies! And it wasn't released outside of Japan for almost 15 years. At some point it was considered the best Castlevania ever  and I think everyone thought alike until Symphony of the Night. So basically  a lost jewell for the western world. There was a remake in the SNES but it was actually a complete different game. It was possible to play it as an unlockable game in The Dracula X Chronicles... But now we are going to be able to enjoy the original game for the first time  on the Turbografx-16 mini!!! So  the first videos are an amazing intro animation. The voice translation is: "Long ago people lived in peace and harmony. No one noticed the looming shadow among them. Their senses clouded in darkness  evil ate away at their souls. In the late hour they congregate to call the powers of Satan with sinful blood to save them from their mortal existence. Evis has once again been made flesh. He can become a bat  fog  or wolf and feasts on human blood. Lord of darkness  master of Castlevania  Dracula walk among us." This game has a fantastic soundtrack  making use of the CD-Rom capacity for better sound quality. There's a 2CD OST released with music from this game and also from Castlevania Bloodlines. Treccani si occupa di Death Stranding. Di più  lo fa fare al direttore del VIGAMUS  il Museo del Videogioco. Un'occasione incredibile per rivendicare un minimo di riconoscimento culturale per la nostra forma di intrattenimento preferita.  Peccato che ne venga fuori un pezzo dove i videogiochi vengono costantemente messi a paragone con il cinema.  Così le ambizioni registiche di Kojima in Death Stranding sono esasperate "complice il coinvolgimento di numerosi attori"  poco importa se invece l'idea è che il gameplay sia racconto  non solo raccordo.  Così coinvolgere attori famosi in un videogioco è una "scelta suicida" perché in un videogioco non può emergere la loro personalità  e un game designer non può improvvisarsi regista.  Il Direttore del Museo del Videogioco insomma subordina il videogioco al cinema per buona parte delle 1600 parole dell'articolo.  È l'unico modo per rendere i videogiochi "cultura alta". Se non ci crede nemmeno lui  chi deve crederci? DDR4 a 5 GHz e Ryzen 9 3900X: l’overclocker der8auer testa un inedito kit di Gigabyte - L’overclocker Roman “der8auer” Hartung ha messo alla prova su piattaforma X570 con Ryzen 9 3900X un inedito kit di memoria DDR4-5000 di Gigabyte. L’azienda ci sta lavorando internamente da un po’ di tempo  tanto che all’ultima Gamescom di agosto aveva promesso a der8auer che presto gli avrebbe inviato qualcosa di speciale. Detto  fatto. Il regalo è arrivato e l’overclocker ha ovviamente messo tutto alla prova in un video che potete vedere qui di seguito. I moduli hanno funzionato a 5 GHz senza richiedere particolari interventi o raffreddamento esotici  ma solo l’impostazione di un semplice profilo XMP dal BIOS. É extremamente comum em um jogo você ter vários aspectos que se repetem  inimigos  objetos no cenário  itens e etc.  Por isso também é bastante comum nós podermos generalizar essas coisas e reutiliza-lás. … Pegue o exemplo de um personagem principal  ele vai estar EM TODAS AS FASES! Kkkk Agora imagine o fluxo -> Criar uma cena nova -> Colocar um SKSpriteNode -> Colocar a textura do personagem -> Seta as animações -> Os componentes -> Roda o jogo  Agora pense que seu jogo tem 30 fases distintas… Isso irá se repetir 30 vezes  kkkk.  Pior… Na 27 fase você percebeu que a escala podia ser melhorada  aumentar só um pouquinho  você terá que voltar em cada fase e ajustar isso  certo?  Pois bem  chega de fazer as coisas no Go horsing… trago a vocês a tal solução… SKReferenceNode Esse lindo  é um node que simplesmente é uma referência a uma outra cena! Então numa cena podemos fazer o personagem principal e em todas as outras 30 só referenciaremos ela. Relaxa que não pesa já que é só uma referência! E você também pode modificar a vontade dentro de uma cena específica se quiser algo especializado para tal cena  ou modificar na cena “mestre” e assim em todos os lugares que ela estiver sendo referenciada a modificação será aplicada! Per quanto possa essere un nuovo soulslike  Code Vein si conferma come un prodotto dall’anima originale e complessa  sfruttando l’estetica giapponese per proporre una delle esperienze più divertenti del genere. Attraverso a un sistema tanto accessibile quanto profondo e malleabile  vivere i panni di un Redivivo diventa una sfida più che gustosa che può essere adattata a qualsiasi tipo di giocatore. Ma il combattimento non è l’unico elemento invitante del gioco: la trama coinvolgente – anche grazie a un editor più che ottimo – e il ricco cast sono solo la portata principale di un mondo fatto di misteri  ricordi e colpi di scena sconvolgenti. Nonostante qualche comprensibile difetto  Bandai Namco e le menti dietro God Eater sono riusciti a produrre una nuova formula vincente  facendo nascere un’esperienza che si fa decisamente perdonare della lunga attesa.⠀ La mia Recensione di Code Vein per Game Division!⠀ -⠀ -⠀ #codevein #bandainamco #anime #vampire #soulslike #pc #ps4 #playstation #nintendoswitch #sony #xbox #mcirosoft #gamingfolk #gaming #gamer #game #videogame #videogames #videogioco #videogiochi #nerd #geek #singleplayer #multiplayer #player #playing #play #gamereview #recensione

Zelda Link’s Awakening – это ремейк классической Зельды с видом сверху  выпущенной ещё в далёком 1993 году на #GameBoy. На #NintendoSwitch игра перенесена практически с учётом всех нюансов  с улучшением графики и управления. Эта забота одновременно и плюс и минус игры. Бывалые геймеры будут рады и вспомнят былые времена  когда каждый секрет в подобных РПГ решался далеко не сразу и приходилось пробегать всю карту в течении нескольких часов  чтобы наконец понять  что и куда дальше. Но сегодняшние геймеры скорее назовут это проблемой геймдизайна  но никак не фишкой игры.  Что касается меня  то проблемы при прохождении я испытал буквально пару тройку раз. И это не проблемы с загадками в подземельях (они то как раз здесь очень крутые и их интересно решать именно самому)  а практически всегда это был вопрос «Куда же идти дальше?» Порой игра даёт лишь мелкие подсказки  которые не всегда очевидны. Решал это с помощью гайда для версии игры 1993 года (благо вся карта перенесена в ремейк 1 в 1) и зазрения совести от этого не испытываю. Пробегать всю карту и рубить мечом каждый кустик в надежде  что вот сейчас то под этим будет секретный вход в нужное подземелье… время дороже и времена не те :) В целом  ремейк однозначно понравился. Особо хочется отметить графику и стилистику проекта. Эстетика пластиковых игрушек выглядит замечательно  мир и персонажи очаровывают. #LinksAwakening способна вернуть вас в детство  даже если вы не играли в оригинал. А #Switch получил ещё один отличный эксклюзив в свою библиотеку.  #zelda #nintendoswitchgames #nintendo #linkzelda #portablegaming #rpggames #videogames #consolegaming #консольныеигры #видеоигры #обзорыигр #games #gaminglife

Comodidad en mi desorden Al principio crei que era una completa basura  debia entregarlo rapido y queria trabajar en un soporte de tela  pero con el tiempo al cuello tuve que ultilizar lo que mas rapido encontré  carton. Cuando lo terminé  el acrílico no se secaba y encima se resbalaba  intente arreglarlo pero cada vez empeoraba mas. Lo dejé así  lo entregué así.  Me rehusaba a aceptar que ese desastre era mío y de mala gana se lo mostré a mi profesora  ella dijo que la idea de la imagen (la cual habia ultilizado para hacer esta "obra") era mostrar lo íntimo  entre uno y uno  las cosas tiradas arriba de la mesa así nomas  los paquetes de pizzas de hace días aun ahí arriba  el videojuego que nos entretiene  todo era parte e iba en conjunto con el carton como soporte  porque el carton aumentaba aun mas la forma del desorden.  La idea del desorden siempre esta dentro de los parametros de nuestro orden  siempre esta ahi para desorganizar un poco y darse cuenta que uno está dejándose llevar  el desorden nos da orden. No obstante el orden a veces da placer  pero ¿porqué el desorden tampoco lo daría? No le teman a creer en el desorden como orden descomunal de lo monótono  obras en tela hay demasiadas pero pocas en cartón que se apeguen tanto a la idea. . . .  No me pregunten que carajo quise decir. . . #art #naturalezamuerta #arte #carton #acrylicpainting #print #painting #donkeykong #pizza #game #videogames

30 settembre 1988 IBM annuncia l'avvenuta spedizione di 3 milioni di personal computer PS/2. Il PS/2 succede alle serie PC  PC/XT e PC/AT ed utilizza la Micro Channel Architecture  un formato di bus incompatibile con lo standard ISA  adottato dai costruttori di cloni. IBM aveva presentato le sue macchine PS/2 solo l'anno prima  facendo in modo che le unità disco per floppy da 3 pollici e ½ e la VGA (Video Graphic Array) divenissero degli standard per i computer IBM ed i compatibili. I PS/2 sono stati i primi computer IBM ad utilizzare il chip 80386 di Intel ed il nuovo sistema operativo OS/2  consentendo l'utilizzo di un mouse con i computer IBM. #retroday #noiche #1980s #apple #atari #8bit #16bit #commodore #amstrad #msx #retrogaming #nerd #retrocomputer #retro #mac #computerhistory #geek #arcade #retrocomputing #videogames #retrogames #vintagecomputer #zxspectrum #vintage #retroconsole #machenesannoiduemila #AccaddeOggi #OnThisDay

We had a jammed packed Saturday! Days like this when we go  go  go I worry how Collin is going to function in a new place.  The company Richard works for had a Carnival day for employees and their families. It was a blast! Between food trucks and carnival performers  you can't go wrong.  As always  arriving at a new place it takes Collin a little awhile to get out of the Jeep. We typically set a timer so he knows that once the timer goes off we need to get out of the Jeep. I typically can tell when Collin is anxious about going to a new place because he will start to perseverate on something...today it was snacks.  We did bring his Ipad just in case it was too overwhelming for him. I now have been trained to automatically pick up what will contribute to sensory overload. There were plenty... But we take it at Collin's pace and that seems to work for him. I'm pretty sure he had a good time! He loved the dunk tank and participated in dunking one of Richard's manager and the president of the company 😉  We ended the day with a birthday party for one of Jonah's friends  Liam...friends since VPK!! The party was at a local place called The District - arcade  and bowling! All the kiddos had an amazing time!! It was nice to see Collin like every other kid  having fun playing video games...I definitely could tell after he was done playing games he was starting to have a sensory overload. He was very excited not knowing where to look or what he wanted to play...and he wanted to touch EVERYTHING! He played a handful of games and did really well  but as the evening progressed I could tell he was done. He started stimming  flapping and rocking back and forth. At that point  all the kids had burned through their game cards and it we called it a night and headed home. . . . #autismmoments #autismsiblingsrock #autismlove #differntnotless #autismjourney #autismfamily #asd  #autism #autismacceptance #autismmom #autismdad  #autisminthecommunity #autismstar #autismwarrior  #specialneedsmom #specialneedsparenting #specialneedskids #advocate  #carnivalfun #foodtrucks #zebraballoonanimals #videogames #boutiquebowling #thedistrictoviedo

🎮 BARCODE BATTLERS II 時空を超えた戦士たち (Warriors who travelled in time) . Barcode Battlers was a series of Handheld consoles made by Epoch. . Barcode scanning toys and arcade games were extremely popular in the 90's Japan including the Datach Famicom add on  the later Digivices and Barcode Wars by Bandai. The strength of the Barcode Wars series was its connection to nintendo  allowing them to make exclusive barcode games with nintendo franchise such as Mario Bros and Zelda. . It also allowed players connect to their Super Famicom or original Gameboy via the 'Barcode Boy' to send data from the barcode cards into the Barcode Battler console games. . Barcode Battler was highly successful in Japan and even saw a release of western versions with alternative art and characters. . The two biggest mistakes I see Mercy players make are 1. Using Rez without checking position. There’s a difference between a risky rez and a rez that was always going to fail.  2. Not preferring targets- a low dps comes before a half health tank. Keep an eye on your other healer. You can usually allow an off tank to die for the sake of your main (unless your zar is very charged or something). Flick your beam to characters who are frontlining or about to take damage. La primera vez que fuimos ahí tenía 15 años  es la primera vez que recuerdo haber estado ahí. Fue catastrófico: terminé hablándole con violencia a alguien que amenazaba la paz de mi primer amor  jaja justo a mi me iba a pelear?! De haber sabido que era de una de las familias más peligrosas de ese entonces quizás hubiese sido distinto  no lo sé  pero si una cosa supe siempre es que no dejaría que nadie dañe a alguien que quiero.  Las siguientes veces no las recuerdo  pero la ante última sí  fui empleada  mi primer trabajo. Ahí tuve que sacar a la luz simpatía  responsabilidad  frialdad  y más violencia. Terminé peleando con un chico  dos veces  y la última gané yo  no por fuerza  sino que él estaba tan drogado (y por ahí no tanto  porque hasta planeó ir con alguien para afanarme) que no podía ni iba responder luego de que le removí la mandíbula de un derechazo.  Y de las últimas fueron visitando amigas que hice ahí. Siempre un mate  y un poco de metegol o pool para no perder la costumbre. Persona 3 – Beat: 11 November 2007 Time: 129: 30 Persona 3 – The Journey – Beat: 5 November 2010 Time: 64: 11  I remember the summer of 2007. There was no expectation for another release from Atlus. I was already acquainted with the world of Persona and MegaTen  so at that point only Atlus fans and the odd weirdo were looking forward to this.  I had pre-ordered it at GameStop and they didn't get it until Thursday of release week (Games and movies were released on Tuesdays). I played it for a few months and those blue screens and menus and music blended with the long hazy days of late summer  the chilly nights of mid autumn  and the frozen reverberations of winter chill.  I still have mixed feelings about this game. But is it a good game? Yup! I'd play the PSP port in a heartbeat if I find a reasonable priced copy.  #persona3 #persona3fes #persona #atlus #atlususa #megaten #playstation2 #ps2 #PlayStation #jrpg #rpg #roleplayinggames #classicgames #instagaming #videogames #gamecollection #smt #shinmegamitensei #megamitensei

(45) “What’s wrong?” Abram snaps out of his rumination to turn to Cassandra who’s been intensely eyeing him. “What do you mean?” Cassandra  “Is it something that the villager said?” Abram shakes his head  “All he said is that we need to reach his son for a potion that will relieve his wife’s illness.” Cassandra  “Will it require grounded fungus and skeletal remains infused with demonic essence?” Abram scoffs  “The potion is suppose to help her breath  not infect her.” Cassandra  “Then why are you standing there looking so grave?” Abram ease the tension on his face to give a half-hearted grin  “I was thinking about.…about my parents.” Cassandra  “I can have Harding send a missive to Haven to see if Leliana received word from Ostwick.” Abram  “Thank you but not necessary.” Cassandra  “If that will give you a peace of mind to focus on…” Abram interrupts  “Any more news on the horse master?” Cassandra  “The farm remained unscathed from the fighting but I don’t know for how long. Give me a moment to talk to Harding…” Abram cuts her off  “Clearing the West Road will help our soldiers gain a foothold of the crossing. We must do so now.” Cassandra resigns with a sigh  “Yes  we should go.” At the corner of her eye  she sees Lucian walking by. Cassandra  “Scout Durand!” Lucian jogs up to Cassandra and bows  “Seeker.” Cassandra  “Gather the others. We’re heading to the West Road. You should also prepare.” Lucian speaks without looking up  “Understood. I just need to make a minor adjustment to my provision.” Cassandra  “Do what you must but do it quick.” “Yes ser.” Without a pause  Lucian dashes off. Abram trails Lucian with his eyes  “He seems a little nervous.” Cassandra  “I have faith that he will do well. I believe your siblings have been speaking with Scout Whittle by the entrance. To prepare for the new Modern Warfare i started off with the one that kicked the series into new heights. Bare in mind I played the remaster version. This is a solid game even in today standards. A short but impactful campaign that has good Characters  great set pieces and tight gameplay. In terms of arcade action you can't get any better then this. The multiplayer is as good as it's always been with the creating a class and adding attachments and skins. There are problems of course. First off the loot box system is horrible. I hate it and screw Activision for putting it in here and screw them harder for making dlc maps for a remaster...dlc. Activision really don't care. And for me I played it through veteran and I get it. It's hardest difficulty but you do sometimes feel really unfair. I lost count how many times I'd fight the same enemy after a checkpoint restart and it always be random if I'd have time to shoot him or he'd snap to me and kill me quicker then I can aim down sight's. Our felt very unfair. Apart from that the game is great and set in stone a series that would make way for a generation of gamers. But what did you guys and gals think? Let me know and I'll see you guys... In the next post.  #game #Games #gaming #videogame #videogames #callofduty #callofduty4modernwarfare #callofduty4remastered
